message.body: Its Gracie - your mom brought my stuff to you. I'm wondering when will be a good time for me to pick it up. This week is sort of hectic but let me know.
Hey Gracie, anytime early next week would be good for me
Would Wednesday work or is that too late into the week?
Anytime - its a small car so maybe I'll need two trips but whenever
Hey Noah - am wondering what time tomorrow is good for you and where you live. Thanks!
